### Medium OAuth - Connect
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/medium/connect
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "brand": "{{brandId}}"
}

### Medium OAuth - Verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/medium/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "{{authCode}}",
  "state": "{{state}}"
}

### Medium - Publish Article
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/medium/publish/{{articleId}}?brandId={{brandId}}&publishStatus=public
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

